subject: Tour de France (Bicycle Race)
Bicycles and Bicycling
lead_paragraph: Levi Leipheimer, who won last year’s Tour De France final time trial, won the fifth stage of the Tour of California by 29 seconds over David Millar, the British time-trial champion.
